37105>>>>>    
37105>>>>>    //
37105>>>>>    // This procedure is called when validating a session and after logging in. Its purpose is to 
37105>>>>>    // update properties based on the session and user data. Augment this function to update 
37105>>>>>    // properties based on the session / user table. Note that WebAppUser and WebAppSession contain
37105>>>>>    // the right records when this procedure is called.
37105>>>>>    //
37105>>>>>    // Params:
37105>>>>>    //      bClear   True if the procedure is called before session validation to clear properties.
37105>>>>>    //
37105>>>>>    Procedure UpdateSessionProperties Boolean bClear
37107>>>>>        Handle hoUserDD
37107>>>>>        
37107>>>>>        Get phoUserDD to hoUserDD
37108>>>>>        
37108>>>>>        //  Update user properties
37108>>>>>        If (not(bClear) and HasRecord(hoUserDD)) Begin
37110>>>>>            Set psUsername to (Trim(WebAppUser.FullName))
37111>>>>>            Set psLoginName to (Trim(WebAppUser.LoginName))
37112>>>>>            Set piUserRights to WebAppUser.Rights
37113>>>>>            
37113>>>>>            Send OnSessionPropertiesSet 
37114>>>>>        End
37114>>>>>>
37114>>>>>        Else Begin
37115>>>>>            Set psUsername to ""
37116>>>>>            Set psLoginName to ""
37117>>>>>            Set piUserRights to 0
37118>>>>>            
37118>>>>>            Send OnSessionPropertiesClear
37119>>>>>        End
37119>>>>>>
37119>>>>>    End_Procedure
37120>>>>>    
37120>>>>>    Procedure OnSessionPropertiesSet
37122>>>>>        //  Empty event stub
37122>>>>>    End_Procedure
37123>>>>>    
37123>>>>>    Procedure OnSessionPropertiesClear
37125>>>>>        //  Empty event stub
37125>>>>>    End_Procedure
37126>>>>>    
37126>>>>>    Procedure EndSession
37128>>>>>        Integer iErr
37128>>>>>        Boolean bLogWebSession
37128>>>>>        Handle hoSessionDD       
37128>>>>>        
37128>>>>>        Get phoSessionDD to hoSessionDD
37129>>>>>        Get pbLogWebSession to bLogWebSession
37130>>>>>        If not bLogWebSession Begin
37132>>>>>            Forward Send EndSession
37134>>>>>            Procedure_Return
37135>>>>>        End
37135>>>>>>
37135>>>>>            
37135>>>>>        //  Check if session exists
37135>>>>>        Send Clear of hoSessionDD
37136>>>>>        Get psSessionKey to WebAppSession.SessionKey
37137>>>>>        
37137>>>>>        Send Find of hoSessionDD EQ Index.1
37138>>>>>        If (Found) Begin
37140>>>>>            Set Field_Changed_Value of hoSessionDD Field WebAppSession.Active to "N"
37141>>>>>            Get Request_Validate of hoSessionDD to iErr
37142>>>>>            If (iErr) Begin
37144>>>>>                // this should not happen. If it does its a programming error
37144>>>>>                Error DFERR_PROGRAM C_$WebAppSessionValidateFailed
37145>>>>>>
37145>>>>>                Procedure_Return
37146>>>>>            End
37146>>>>>>
37146>>>>>            Send Request_Save of hoSessionDD
37147>>>>>        End
37147>>>>>>
37147>>>>>    End_Procedure
37148>>>>>
37148>>>>>End_Class
